19
00:00:54.050 --> 00:00:57.750
First Officer's Log.

20
00:00:54.050 --> 00:00:57.750
Stardate 1224.3.

21
00:00:57.850 --> 00:01:00.410
The Enterprise has arrived at Hetemit 9.

22
00:01:00.490 --> 00:01:04.020
the site of an abandoned

23
00:01:00.490 --> 00:01:04.020
Illyrian colony.

24
00:01:04.090 --> 00:01:07.590
Illyrians are a humanoid species

25
00:01:04.090 --> 00:01:07.590
