43
00:01:44.870 --> 00:01:46.430
Damn it. I wish we had more time.

44
00:01:46.540 --> 00:01:48.090
These shelters are pretty old.

45
00:01:46.540 --> 00:01:48.090
We should get everyone back

46
00:01:48.200 --> 00:01:49.830
