71
00:03:18.030 --> 00:03:19.650
Ops personnel to Deck 16.

72
00:03:33.640 --> 00:03:35.910
Engineering to Transporter. Try it now.

73
00:03:37.050 --> 00:03:38.740
What the... How did you...

74
00:03:39.250 --> 00:03:41.240
I am a genius. Move quickly.

75
00:03:42.020 --> 00:03:43.110
Copy.

76
00:03:50.260 --> 00:03:52.020
Better not be out of miracles. Mr. Kyle.

77
00:03:52.130 --> 00:03:54.390
Captain and Mr. Spock

78
00:03:52.130 --> 00:03:54.390
