83
00:04:06.780 --> 00:04:08.440
- I'm looking forward to reading them.

84
00:04:06.780 --> 00:04:08.440
- Great.

85
00:04:08.510 --> 00:04:09.840
How about we get to the rendezvous point

86
00:04:09.950 --> 00:04:11.710
