88
00:04:20.720 --> 00:04:22.550
Pike to Enterprise. Two to beam up.

89
00:04:29.530 --> 00:04:31.020
I can't get a lock.

90
00:04:31.100 --> 00:04:33.130
- Pull more power.

91
00:04:31.100 --> 00:04:33.130
