100
00:04:47.620 --> 00:04:49.080
Suggestions. Mr. Spock?

101
00:04:49.150 --> 00:04:50.140
Run.

102
00:04:58.560 --> 00:04:59.690
Space.

103
00:05:01.530 --> 00:05:03.520
The final frontier.

104
00:05:06.100 --> 00:05:09.130
These are the voyages

105
00:05:06.100 --> 00:05:09.130
