118
00:07:07.590 --> 00:07:10.180
Cadet Uhura. can you get a signal?

119
00:07:10.290 --> 00:07:11.820
No. Commander.

120
00:07:11.930 --> 00:07:15.300
The ion storm is functionally

121
00:07:11.930 --> 00:07:15.300
a communications blackout.

122
00:07:15.430 --> 00:07:17.330
I want to know the second

123
00:07:15.430 --> 00:07:17.330
