124
00:07:17.800 --> 00:07:19.290
Yes. Commander.

125
00:07:19.370 --> 00:07:20.360
Lieutenant Wheeler.

126
00:07:20.440 --> 00:07:22.200
I want round-the-clock

127
00:07:20.440 --> 00:07:22.200
