128
00:07:22.300 --> 00:07:24.400
The second it starts to let up.

129
00:07:22.300 --> 00:07:24.400
I want to know.

130
00:07:24.470 --> 00:07:26.200
And tell Chief Kyle

131
00:07:24.470 --> 00:07:26.200
