132
00:07:26.270 --> 00:07:27.900
I want the transporter standing by.

133
00:07:35.820 --> 00:07:36.840
Ensign Lance?

134
00:07:36.920 --> 00:07:38.080
Are you all right?

135
00:07:38.150 --> 00:07:39.620
It's too dark in here.

136
00:07:40.220 --> 00:07:42.660
Okay. it's been a long day

137
00:07:40.220 --> 00:07:42.660
