143
00:07:51.830 --> 00:07:53.890
Whatever tweaks your freak. pal.

144
00:07:56.970 --> 00:07:58.340
What the hell are you doing?

145
00:07:58.410 --> 00:07:59.400
Ortegas to Security.

146
00:07:59.470 --> 00:08:01.070
