147
00:08:18.590 --> 00:08:21.090
Computer. increase illumination 25%.

148
00:08:53.290 --> 00:08:54.790
Number One to Dr. M'Benga.

149
00:08:54.860 --> 00:08:57.260
What is the status of the landing party?

150
00:08:57.370 --> 00:09:00.030
Good evening. Commander.

151
00:08:57.370 --> 00:09:00.030
Funny you should mention it.

152
00:09:00.570 --> 00:09:02.330
I have several of them in here

153
00:09:00.570 --> 00:09:02.330
