154
00:09:02.440 --> 00:09:04.600
presenting with some

155
00:09:02.440 --> 00:09:04.600
very curious symptoms.

156
00:09:04.670 --> 00:09:07.840
I was about to call you.

157
00:09:04.670 --> 00:09:07.840
Are you feeling all right?

158
00:09:07.980 --> 00:09:09.470
I'm okay.

159
00:09:09.540 --> 00:09:12.540
Better come down here and let me

160
00:09:09.540 --> 00:09:12.540
