161
00:09:13.520 --> 00:09:14.640
On my way.

162
00:09:28.000 --> 00:09:29.060
It's odd.

163
00:09:29.600 --> 00:09:32.690
Half of them have burned

164
00:09:29.600 --> 00:09:32.690
