168
00:09:38.710 --> 00:09:41.800
They're being attracted

169
00:09:38.710 --> 00:09:41.800
to light.

170
00:09:41.880 --> 00:09:45.280
So much so they're willing

171
00:09:41.880 --> 00:09:45.280
