174
00:09:50.190 --> 00:09:51.280
No.

175
00:09:52.520 --> 00:09:54.320
You found nothing else in their systems?

176
00:09:54.390 --> 00:09:55.690
No form of contagion?

177
00:09:56.060 --> 00:09:57.720
Well. the transporter's biofilters

178
00:09:57.830 --> 00:09:59.850
would have screened out

179
00:09:57.830 --> 00:09:59.850
