180
00:09:59.930 --> 00:10:03.300
But I ran viral and bacterial

181
00:09:59.930 --> 00:10:03.300
scans anyway as a precaution.

182
00:10:03.930 --> 00:10:05.160
They're clean.

183
00:10:05.730 --> 00:10:09.230
Only thing I've been able to find

184
00:10:05.730 --> 00:10:09.230
