185
00:10:11.110 --> 00:10:12.510
Vitamin D?

186
00:10:13.880 --> 00:10:15.840
All show levels in the red.

187
00:10:15.940 --> 00:10:18.410
Outside of this

188
00:10:15.940 --> 00:10:18.410
and the aberrant behavior.

189
00:10:19.310 --> 00:10:20.910
you'd never know they were sick.

190
00:10:21.020 --> 00:10:22.510
How were my vitamin D levels?

191
00:10:23.250 --> 00:10:24.510
Normal.

192
00:10:24.850 --> 00:10:27.790
Whatever affected them

193
00:10:24.850 --> 00:10:27.790
seems to have missed you.

194
00:10:29.260 --> 00:10:31.890
I'd like to take a blood sample

195
00:10:29.260 --> 00:10:31.890
nonetheless.

196
00:10:32.860 --> 00:10:34.260
Commander?

197
00:10:34.360 --> 00:10:35.560
Of course.

198
00:10:36.460 --> 00:10:39.060
Have you been able to reach

199
00:10:36.460 --> 00:10:39.060
the captain and Mr. Spock?

200
00:10:40.140 --> 00:10:42.300
Still too much interference

201
00:10:40.140 --> 00:10:42.300
