204
00:10:48.080 --> 00:10:50.380
I have to believe the landing

205
00:10:48.080 --> 00:10:50.380
party came into contact

206
00:10:50.480 --> 00:10:53.280
with something down there

207
00:10:50.480 --> 00:10:53.280
