216
00:11:04.630 --> 00:11:07.430
What about the ion storm?

217
00:11:04.630 --> 00:11:07.430
Could that have interfered with it?

218
00:11:07.530 --> 00:11:09.330
- No.

219
00:11:10.130 --> 00:11:11.360
I mean...

220
00:11:12.200 --> 00:11:13.460
