228
00:11:26.580 --> 00:11:27.740
No.

229
00:11:28.350 --> 00:11:30.080
I can sense that expression. you know.

230
00:11:30.190 --> 00:11:31.350
Oh. I know.

231
00:11:32.550 --> 00:11:35.550
You had to pull a lot of power

232
00:11:32.550 --> 00:11:35.550
