238
00:11:42.130 --> 00:11:44.660
the new systems have

239
00:11:42.130 --> 00:11:44.660
discrete backups for biofilters

240
00:11:44.730 --> 00:11:46.130
and pattern stabilizers.

241
00:11:48.440 --> 00:11:52.240
I will run a Level 5 diagnostic

242
00:11:48.440 --> 00:11:52.240
