243
00:11:53.140 --> 00:11:55.370
- To make you feel better. Commander.

244
00:11:53.140 --> 00:11:55.370
- Thank you.

245
00:11:55.440 --> 00:11:58.310
Which. I might add.

246
00:11:55.440 --> 00:11:58.310
