247
00:11:59.280 --> 00:12:01.880
Decontamination crew.

248
00:11:59.280 --> 00:12:01.880
Transporter Room 3.

249
00:12:01.950 --> 00:12:03.710
Only Level 2 protocol...

250
00:12:11.130 --> 00:12:12.350
On screen.

251
00:12:12.960 --> 00:12:14.190
Number One?

252
00:12:14.300 --> 00:12:16.420
Are you and Lieutenant Spock all right?

253
00:12:16.500 --> 00:12:18.830
We're fine. but the storm has

254
00:12:16.500 --> 00:12:18.830
