270
00:12:53.070 --> 00:12:54.760
Records are limited.

271
00:12:57.840 --> 00:12:59.330
You wanted to see me. Chief?

272
00:13:00.170 --> 00:13:02.940
Yes. Several landing party members

273
00:13:03.010 --> 00:13:06.140
