281
00:13:17.660 --> 00:13:19.690
I don't know what to think.

282
00:13:17.660 --> 00:13:19.690
I'm just doing research.

283
00:13:19.790 --> 00:13:22.230
Well. it seems to me.

284
00:13:19.790 --> 00:13:22.230
things like this are exactly

285
00:13:22.330 --> 00:13:25.630
