00:39:32.700 --> 00:39:33.890
Not what.

875
00:39:35.870 --> 00:39:36.960
Who.

876
00:39:37.440 --> 00:39:38.740
Rukiya.

877
00:39:43.040 --> 00:39:44.530
My daughter.

878
00:39:44.840 --> 00:39:47.370
A year ago. she was diagnosed

879
00:39:44.840 --> 00:39:47.370
with cygnokemia.

880
00:39:48.010 --> 00:39:49.380
Brutal disease.

881
00:39:51.890 --> 00:39:54.950
You can't imagine what it's like

882
00:39:51.890 --> 00:39:54.950
to watch your child wither away.

883
00:39:57.320 --> 00:40:00.920
To see a lifetime of potential

884
00:39:57.320 --> 00:40:00.920
reduced to a 12-week prognosis.

885
00:40:02.330 --> 00:40:03.630
I'm sorry.

886
00:40:04.330 --> 00:40:06.300
I am Chief Medical Officer.

887
00:40:08.330 --> 00:40:10.500
On the flagship of Starfleet.

888
00:40:12.640 --> 00:40:15.270
You'd think I'd be able to do

889
00:40:12.640 --> 00:40:15.270
something about it.

890
00:40:18.540 --> 00:40:19.810
But nothing worked.

891
00:40:21.250 --> 00:40:23.180
Did you know there's no limit

892
00:40:23.950 --> 00:40:26.920
on how long you can store

893
00:40:23.950 --> 00:40:26.920
someone's pattern in the buffer?

894
00:40:30.220 --> 00:40:33.090
You just have to materialize

895
00:40:30.220 --> 00:40:33.090
them regularly.

896
00:40:35.700 --> 00:40:37.890
In the buffer. my daughter doesn't age.

897
00:40:39.370 --> 00:40:41.330
And her disease can't progress.

898
00:40:42.500 --> 00:40:44.530
We travel light-years in hours.

899
00:40:45.840 --> 00:40:47.600
And somewhere out there

900
00:40:49.540 --> 00:40:51.910
is a planet that has

901
00:40:49.540 --> 00:40:51.910
the discovery I need.

902
00:40:53.080 --> 00:40:54.070
Only.

903
00:40:56.180 --> 00:40:58.580
the light virus epidemic was my fault.

904
00:40:59.790 --> 00:41:01.350
It seems so. yes.

905
00:41:02.760 --> 00:41:04.950
If I thought. even for a second.

906
00:41:05.430 --> 00:41:06.980
that could have happened...

907
00:41:08.700 --> 00:41:10.430
It won't happen again.

908
00:41:12.800 --> 00:41:15.270
I can't endanger our crew for one life.

909
00:41:16.400 --> 00:41:18.740
No matter how much

910
00:41:16.400 --> 00:41:18.740
that life means to me.

911
00:41:21.610 --> 00:41:22.840
But I ask.

912
00:41:24.610 --> 00:41:26.010
would you consider.

913
00:41:26.680 --> 00:41:28.670
before you return me to Starfleet.

914
00:41:29.220 --> 00:41:32.670
that I might have a chance to spend

915
00:41:29.220 --> 00:41:32.670
a little more time with my daughter?

916
00:41:38.160 --> 00:41:39.420
To say goodbye.

917
00:41:41.160 --> 00:41:42.150
No.

918
00:41:45.530 --> 00:41:48.660
I'll provide a dedicated power source.

919
00:41:45.530 --> 00:41:48.660
direct from the warp core.

920
00:41:50.640 --> 00:41:51.830
This problem?

921
00:41:52.710 --> 00:41:55.000
We can ensure it never happens again.

922
00:42:03.080 --> 00:42:05.140
I look forward to meeting her one day.

923
00:42:13.060 --> 00:42:14.890
First Officer's personal log.

924
00:42:18.770 --> 00:42:20.360
The lights are back on.

925
00:42:20.870 --> 00:42:22.930
But that doesn't mean we see clearly.

926
00:42:24.400 --> 00:42:26.130
People are always hiding things.

927
00:42:35.380 --> 00:42:37.580
Hi. Dad. Story time?

928
00:42:38.720 --> 00:42:39.950
You bet.

929
00:42:40.820 --> 00:42:41.880
Now. where were we?

930
00:42:41.950 --> 00:42:43.860
King Ridley was about to climb the tower

931
00:42:43.920 --> 00:42:46.220
to rescue Princess Thalia

932
00:42:43.920 --> 00:42:46.220
from evil Queen Neve.

933
00:42:46.290 --> 00:42:48.120
Wait.

934
00:42:48.900 --> 00:42:50.450
No spoilers.

935
00:42:51.030 --> 00:42:53.900
Dad. you've read this.

936
00:42:51.030 --> 00:42:53.900
like. a hundred times.

937
00:42:54.000 --> 00:42:57.600
That doesn't mean that the ending

938
00:42:54.000 --> 00:42:57.600
couldn't miraculously change.

939
00:42:57.700 --> 00:42:59.830
Dr. M'Benga stopped hiding today.

940
00:42:59.940 --> 00:43:01.170
just a little.

941
00:43:01.270 --> 00:43:02.300
And for once.

942
00:43:02.840 --> 00:43:04.040
I did. too.

943
00:43:06.710 --> 00:43:09.440
I told Captain Pike

944
00:43:06.710 --> 00:43:09.440
the truth about myself.

945
00:43:11.020 --> 00:43:12.420
And he defended me.

946
00:43:13.390 --> 00:43:15.150
Told me I was exemplary.

947
00:43:15.250 --> 00:43:17.020
That he would fight for me.

948
00:43:21.060 --> 00:43:22.790
So why do I feel terrible?

949
00:43:27.600 --> 00:43:30.040
What if I hadn't saved all those lives?

950
00:43:32.000 --> 00:43:33.600
Would the captain feel the same?

951
00:43:36.610 --> 00:43:38.700
What would he do if I wasn't a hero?

952
00:43:38.780 --> 00:43:40.010
One of the "good ones"?

953
00:43:42.320 --> 00:43:44.510
When will it be enough to just

954
00:43:46.850 --> 00:43:48.220
be an Illyrian?

955
00:43:54.160 --> 00:43:55.820
- Computer.

956
00:44:01.370 --> 00:44:02.630
Delete log entry.

957
00:44:02.700 --> 00:44:04.140
Log entry deleted.

958
00:44:05.040 --> 00:44:08.200
If King Ridley would seek out

959
00:44:05.040 --> 00:44:08.200
the Mercury Stone

960
00:44:08.310 --> 00:44:09.830
and win it as his own.

961
00:44:10.580 --> 00:44:12.940
his victory over Queen Neve

962
00:44:10.580 --> 00:44:12.940
would be assured.

963
00:44:13.880 --> 00:44:15.850
It is said that in the right hands.

964
00:44:15.920 --> 00:44:19.680
the Mercury Stone has the power

965
00:44:15.920 --> 00:44:19.680
to cleanse the land of evil

966
00:44:20.390 --> 00:44:22.360
and bring prosperity to all.

967
00:44:23.060 --> 00:44:25.650
But if it were to fall

968
00:44:23.060 --> 00:44:25.650
into the wrong hands.

969
00:44:25.760 --> 00:44:30.360
the Mercury Stone's power

970
00:44:25.760 --> 00:44:30.360
would bring about a terrible.

971
00:44:30.830 --> 00:44:34.490
long-lasting dark age across the land.
